title: Matrix Addition
description: Matrix addition is the operation of adding two matrices by adding the corresponding entries together. In this problem, you are given two matrices `A` and `B`, both of dimensions `R x C`. Your task is to compute the sum of these two matrices.
input_format: First line: Two integers R and C. Next R lines: Matrix A. Next R lines: Matrix B.
output_format: Output the resulting `R x C` matrix after addition. Print each row on a new line, with elements in each row separated by spaces.
